  <p>This is why the generic stuff at the pharmacy doesn’t move the needle. It’s only working one side of a two-sided problem&nbsp;—&nbsp;like mopping the floor while the faucet’s still running.</p>

  <p>That’s the science. But what matters more than mechanisms and molecular diagrams is whether this actually works when real people try it&nbsp;—&nbsp;people with 20, 30, 40 years of exposure history. So we put it to the test.</p>

  <h2>The 60-Day Clinical Trial</h2>

  <p>In 2025, BetterLungs&reg;&nbsp;Mullein + Chlorophyll was evaluated in a <strong>randomized, triple-blind, placebo-controlled clinical trial</strong>&nbsp;—&nbsp;the gold standard for supplement research. The study was conducted by Citruslabs with 100 adult participants over 60 days. Assessments were taken at baseline, Day 20, Day 40, and Day 60.</p>

  <p><strong>Here’s what participants in the BetterLungs group reported by Day 60:</strong></p>

  <div class="bl-cr">
    <div class="bl-cr-badge">Clinical Trial Results&nbsp;— 60 Days</div>
    <div class="bl-cr-title">BetterLungs&reg;&nbsp;Mullein + Chlorophyll Drops</div>
    <div class="bl-cr-sub">Randomized, triple-blind, placebo-controlled · 100 participants · Conducted by Citruslabs</div>
    <div class="bl-cr-row">
      <span class="bl-cr-ratio">8 in 10</span>
      <span class="bl-cr-desc">reported <strong>clearer airways</strong> by Day 60</span>
    </div>
    <div class="bl-cr-row">
      <span class="bl-cr-ratio">3 in 4</span>
      <span class="bl-cr-desc">reported it was <strong>easier to clear chest mucus</strong></span>
    </div>
    <div class="bl-cr-row">
