  </div>

  <p>The study also measured fatigue using the validated Fatigue Severity Scale (FSS). <strong>By Day 20, the BetterLungs group showed a statistically significant reduction in fatigue compared to placebo</strong>&nbsp;—&nbsp;a difference that held through Day 60.</p>

